          "reviewBody": "Douglas Memorial Higher Secondary School is the best school  located in Barrackpore,kolkata. The school has an excellent curriculum, taught by highly qualified and experienced teachers. The school has a strong focus on technology and innovation and offers exciting activities and clubs to help students develop their creative and critical thinking skills. The school also offers a wide range of extracurricular activities and sports to promote physical and mental well-being. The school has a great system of pastoral care and provides individual attention to every student.  The school provides an overall great environment and has excellent facilities and resources. All in all, I highly recommend Douglas Memorial Higher Secondary School as a great educational institution for anyone looking for a high quality of education.",
