            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Located next to cantonment board office in Barrackpore. On the lap of nature on barrack road, DMHSS is perfect abode for your child to spend his/her school life. The entrance of the school says half of the story. The in campus space is decorated with beautiful trees and and beautiful props that enhances the holistic development of a child.\nComing to the faculty.... The teachers are well trained with prolong experience in the teaching field. Along with the management body, the teachers take individual care of each and every kid. They believe in not only excellence in academics but also making a child an all-rounder by nurturing his other skills as well.\nThis institution also offers hostel facility for students coming from long distances.",
